pmmd.notes: ML tree inferred from the matK and trnL-F data. The results of ML bootstrap analysis are shown above the branches, whereas the values below the branches result from MP bootstrap analysis. Bootstrap values 450% are shown. The thick branches represent 495% Bayesian posterior probability. *Indicates the nodes not found in the strict consensus tree.
